106
00:06:56,360 --> 00:06:57,460
To be honest,

107
00:06:58,960 --> 00:07:01,670
I wanted to live my life
after my body got young again.

108
00:07:03,830 --> 00:07:05,470
I wanted to play basketball again,

109
00:07:06,940 --> 00:07:08,870
