so let's eat first.

218
00:15:12,560 --> 00:15:13,560
Yes, ma'am.

219
00:15:18,100 --> 00:15:20,030
What are you doing? Eat up.

220
00:15:26,370 --> 00:15:27,440
Thank you.

221
00:15:29,110 --> 00:15:30,110
First,

222
00:15:31,010 --> 00:15:33,640
