that you paid for me.

223
00:15:33,710 --> 00:15:35,010
It's fine.

224
00:15:35,910 --> 00:15:37,250
Eat up. You must be hungry.

225
00:15:37,310 --> 00:15:39,080
You said that you love braised ribs.

226
00:15:39,880 --> 00:15:41,020
Thank you.

227
00:15:51,700 --> 00:15:53,660
