230
00:16:04,470 --> 00:16:06,580
Tell me whenever you want some.

231
00:16:06,640 --> 00:16:08,510
I'll cook for you.

232
00:16:09,610 --> 00:16:10,850
Thank you.

233
00:16:11,820 --> 00:16:13,150
It's nothing.

234
00:16:14,450 --> 00:16:18,390
