699
00:51:54,080 --> 00:51:56,420
Don't you know who she is?

700
00:51:56,880 --> 00:51:58,880
Gosh, no.

701
00:52:00,550 --> 00:52:02,820
I'm a huge fan of hers.

702
00:52:05,220 --> 00:52:07,130
She prepared to become an anchor
at a late age.

703
00:52:07,960 --> 00:52:10,060
So whenever she had job interviews,
it must have been hard,

704
00:52:10,760 --> 00:52:13,200
but she didn't give up and kept trying.

705
00:52:13,900 --> 00:52:16,100
So she got the job
with her 24th interview.

706
00:52:16,170 --> 00:52:17,170
I see.

